                                                                                              SA-11(02)       DEVELOPER TESTING AND EVALUATION | THREAT MODELING AND VULNERABILITY
                                                                                                              ANALYSES
                                                                                                              ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE:
                                                                                                              Determine if:

                                                                                                              SA-11(02)_ODP[01]     informaon concerning impact, environment of operaons, known or assumed
                                                                                                                                    threats, and acceptable risk levels to be used as contextual informaon for threat
                                                                                                                                    modeling and vulnerability analyses is deﬁned;

                                                                                                              SA-11(02)_ODP[02]     the tools and methods to be employed for threat modeling and vulnerability
                                                                                                                                    analyses are deﬁned;

                                                                                                              SA-11(02)_ODP[03]     the breadth and depth of threat modeling to be conducted is deﬁned;

                                                                                                              SA-11(02)_ODP[04]     the breadth and depth of vulnerability analyses to be conducted is deﬁned;

                                                                                                              SA-11(02)_ODP[05]     acceptance criteria to be met by produced evidence for threat modeling are
                                                                                                                                    deﬁned;

                                                                                                              SA-11(02)_ODP[06]     acceptance criteria to be met by produced evidence for vulnerability analyses are
                                                                                                                                    deﬁned;

                                                                                                              SA-11(02)(a)[01]      the developer of the system, system component, or system service is required to
                                                                                                                                    perform threat modeling during development of the system, component, or service
                                                                                                                                    that uses <SA-11(02)_ODP[01] informaon>;

                                                                                                              SA-11(02)(a)[02]      the developer of the system, system component, or system service is required to
                                                                                                                                    perform vulnerability analyses during development of the system, component, or
                                                                                                                                    service that uses <SA-11(02)_ODP[01] informaon>;

                                                                                                              SA-11(02)(a)[03]      the developer of the system, system component, or system service is required
                                                                                                                                    to perform threat modeling during the subsequent tesng and evaluaon of the
                                                                                                                                    system, component, or service that uses <SA-11(02)_ODP[01] informaon>;




